These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, drawing, fishing, sudoku
House: wooden, tower, futuristic, palace, cottage, craftsman
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the tower house is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the cottage house is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the wooden house##2
5. the palace house is between the cottage house and the tower house##2
6. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the wooden house##1
8. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Hobby           | cooking | hiking | sudoku | fishing | drawing    | reading  |
| House   | craftsman | tower   | palace       | cottage        | wooden | futuristic |

