.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
House: cottage, wooden, gothic-revival, tower, art-deco, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, february, december, september, october, may
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the tower house and the cottage house##2
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the cottage house is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the tower house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| House   | wooden | cape-cod | art-deco | tower | gothic-revival | cottage  |
| Birthday           | may | october  | june | february    | september  | december |

