.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: yellow, blue, white, purple, black, ebony
City: prague, paris, liverpool, boston, marseilles, hannover
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person who likes purple is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes black is between the person who likes purple and the person traveling to prague##2
7. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
9. the person who likes blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Color         | blue | yellow | ebony      | black | purple | white      |
| City   | paris    | hannover  | prague | boston   | marseilles       | liverpool |

