2. the indian is on the right of the polish##1
3. the australian is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the egyptian is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is the polish##1
6. the chinese is between the polish and the person watching satire movies##2
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Movie-Genre        | superhero    | satire | action | adventure | family | thriller   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | australian        | chinese  | polish     | indian  | japanese |

