.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, subway, motorbike, taxi, skateboard
City: prague, boston, nizza, hannover, san-francisco, marseilles
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the motorbike and the person traveling to marseilles##2
9. the person driving the trike is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Transport    | trike | skateboard | taxi  | motorbike      | subway | helicopter  |
| City   | boston  | nizza    | hannover | prague | san-francisco | marseilles |

