There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, grey, turquise, light-blue, fuchsia, azure
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes purple##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the train##2
6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Transport           | snowmobile | scooter | train | trike | skateboard | helicopter |
| Color   | turquise   | light-blue   | grey         | purple    | azure     | fuchsia     |

