.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
6 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
There 6 different types of food: lemon, apricot, radish, cabbage, grapes, peas
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person eating lemon is between the owner of the lizard and the person eating peas##2
 3. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Pet   | lizard   | hedgehog  | bird | dog | turtle | cat     |
| Food   | apricot | lemon | peas    | grapes | cabbage | radish |

