5. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes blue and the person who likes pink##2
6. the australian is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the mexican##1
8. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes blue and the nigerian##2
