 4. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating peas and the alhambra-smoker##2
 6. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person eating corn is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is the person eating corn##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is between the person eating corn and the aristoff-smoker##2
10. the davidoff-smoker is the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar         | oliveros   | tiparillo | alhambra       | davidoff | fonseca    | aristoff |
| Food   | peas | cranberry  | broccoli | corn      | tomato | kiwi        |

