.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, rowing, biathlon, baseball, snowboarding
The people use 6 different means of transport: roller, bus, helicopter, taxi, jet-ski, car
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the person driving the car is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is handball##2
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person driving the roller##2
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Sport   | biathlon     | weightlifting | baseball   | rowing     | snowboarding       | handball       |
| Transport    | bus | taxi   | roller | jet-ski | car | helicopter |

