5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
