.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
6 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, rat, cat, hamster, fish
There 6 different types of food: raspberry, banana, grapefruit, pumpkin, mango, nectarine
 1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 7. the person eating banana is the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 9. the person eating grapefruit is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the horse##2
10. the owner of the hamster is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Pet         | cat | horse | guinea-pig | fish | hamster | rat |
| Food   | raspberry | mango | grapefruit      | pumpkin     | nectarine       | banana |

 